but I really wish

01:44.571 --> 01:46.271
I was there in person
to show the dresses

01:46.306 --> 01:48.340
to all the consultants.

01:48.374 --> 01:49.541
I wish you were, too.

01:49.576 --> 01:52.377
But, as soon as we've finished
the renovations

01:52.412 --> 01:53.745
