long to get married.

03:07.687 --> 03:10.689
So, I immediately started
planning the wedding

03:10.723 --> 03:13.692
and found my ceremony dress.

03:13.726 --> 03:16.328
<i>And then my fiance, he's, like,</i>

03:16.362 --> 03:17.529
"Hey, I'm wearing two tuxedos."

03:17.564 --> 03:18.830
So it's like a competition.

03:18.865 --> 03:21.333
<i>So, of course, I have
to keep up with him</i>

03:21.367 --> 03:22.401
<i>and have two dresses.</i>

03:22.435 --> 03:24.169
Typical man.

03:24.204 --> 03:26.972
[upbeat music playing]

03:31.477 --> 03:33.378
Ooh, that's really pretty.

03:38.518 --> 03:43.455
I am here to find the dress
for my reception.

03:43.489 --> 03:46.592
Oh, hmm, oh, oh, cupcake.

03:46.626 --> 03:49.528
<i>I don't have much time
before my wedding,</i>

03:49.562 --> 03:53.298
