has a lot of dresses

03:53.333 --> 03:54.766
and one has my name on it.

03:54.801 --> 03:56.735
But once you say yes
to this dress, honey,

03:56.769 --> 03:58.503
then we got to say yes
to a hairpiece

03:58.538 --> 03:59.738
- and say yes to...
- Yes. Yeah.

03:59.772 --> 04:02.307
- It's yes, yes, and yes.
- ...yes to a veil.

04:02.342 --> 04:04.109
[Candace] Hello, ladies.

04:04.143 --> 04:05.244
Hi.

04:05.278 --> 04:07.246
