they think they're the bride

04:22.695 --> 04:23.495
- and I have to remind them.
- We are.

04:23.529 --> 04:25.764
Because we are all saying yes.

04:25.798 --> 04:28.367
These are my best friends,
Aikisha and Shameika.

04:28.401 --> 04:29.401
- Hi.
- [Candace] Nice to meet you.

04:29.435 --> 04:31.203
Nice to meet you.

04:31.237 --> 04:32.437
Tell me about the wedding.

04:32.472 --> 04:35.240
So, the wedding
is in Atlanta, Georgia.

04:35.275 --> 04:36.375
At Ashton Gardens.

04:36.409 --> 04:37.542
Everyone will be wearing
black...

04:37.577 --> 04:39.077
- [Candace] Mmm-hmm.
- ...except me.

04:39.112 --> 04:40.545
- [Candace] I love black.
- Uninterrupted black,

04:40.580 --> 04:42.347
- all black everything.
- All black everything.

04:42.382 --> 04:44.683
Socks, everything, all black.
Yeah.

04:44.717 --> 04:46.618
