<i>is actually fitted and lace,</i>

04:57.664 --> 05:00.565
<i>and it has lots of drama to it.</i>

05:00.600 --> 05:02.634
- So I want something romantic.
- [Candace] Mmm-hmm.

05:02.669 --> 05:05.637
