tell me the truth.

05:31.631 --> 05:33.432
<i>They're gonna be honest with me.</i>

05:33.466 --> 05:34.766
<i>And, I mean,
they know me the best,</i>

05:34.801 --> 05:38.370
we've known each other
our entire lives.

05:38.404 --> 05:39.471
[Candace] When is the wedding?

05:39.505 --> 05:42.274
Oh, it's six weeks away.

05:42.308 --> 05:43.608
Oh, my gosh. Okay.

05:43.643 --> 05:46.678
Well, now, I'm gonna run
and have a violent panic

05:46.713 --> 05:48.613
- by myself.
- And I'll be waiting.

05:48.648 --> 05:50.582
- [Candace] Okay.
- Okay.

05:50.616 --> 05:54.219
These last-minute brides
send me on a whirlwind.

05:54.253 --> 05:55.520
This is my secret stockroom.

05:55.555 --> 05:56.955
All of these gowns,

05:56.989 --> 05:59.391
she can take home
with her today.

05:59.425 --> 06:02.527
The only challenge
is finding a stock piece

06:02.562 --> 06:04.629
that's actually gonna be
the right style

06:04.664 --> 06:08.767
and the right size.
So I'm really under pressure.

06:08.801 --> 06:10.302
- All right.
- Two to start with

06:10.336 --> 06:11.503
that I really want you to see.

06:11.537 --> 06:13.438
[Stacey] So, I don't care
for this one.

06:13.473 --> 06:14.673
Okay. Keep in mind,

06:14.707 --> 06:15.807
they don't always have
hanger appeal,

06:15.842 --> 06:17.642
