on your body...

06:17.677 --> 06:18.777
- [Stacey] Exactly.
- ...it changes your life.

06:18.811 --> 06:21.780
I do love this one.
I think this looks--

06:21.814 --> 06:24.383
Because I like--
I think I like the texture...

06:24.417 --> 06:25.617
- [Candace] Mmm-hmm.
- ...and it's different.

06:25.651 --> 06:28.120
[Candace] Okay, let's do it.

06:30.523 --> 06:34.059
This dress is one of my
favorite silhouettes.

06:34.093 --> 06:36.661
<i>It has that beautiful
plunging neckline,</i>

06:36.696 --> 06:38.797
<i>it has the flowy bottom
that she really likes.</i>

06:38.831 --> 06:42.501
And it's all about
the details of this dress.

06:42.535 --> 06:45.370
- Don't cry, don't cry, don't cry.
- Mmm-hmm Mmm-hmm. Mmm-hmm.

06:45.405 --> 06:48.140
[upbeat music playing]

06:51.411 --> 06:53.545
- Oh, my God.
- It looks like a yes.

06:53.579 --> 06:54.713
- Yeah.
- [Shameika] Yeah.

06:54.747 --> 06:56.381
See, I like all this
stuff in here.

06:56.416 --> 06:57.449
- I love it.
- [Stacey] Let me show you

06:57.483 --> 06:59.618
- the back first.
- Yes.

06:59.652 --> 07:01.620
- Honey, I love all of that.
- That's beautiful.

