08:31.344 --> 08:32.644
[Alex] Lisa.

08:32.678 --> 08:35.247
- [Lisa] Yes, coming.
- [Alex] Hi.

08:35.281 --> 08:36.648
Hi, beautiful. How are you?

08:36.682 --> 08:38.383
