similar to this.

09:55.728 --> 09:57.495
- And it's a sweetheart?
- [Kellie] Yes.

09:57.530 --> 09:58.630
[Lisa] So you're gonna leave
them here?

09:58.664 --> 10:00.332
Yes, I'm gonna leave them here.

10:00.366 --> 10:01.633
